column2: SELECT sp.specObjID,sp.z, sp.ra,sp.dec, p.decErr, p.raErr, sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS corrpsfmag_u,  sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS corrpsfmag_g,  sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS corrpsfmag_r,  sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS corrpsfmag_i,  sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS corrpsfmag_z, sp.psfMagErr_u, sp.psfMagErr_g, sp.psfMagErr_r,  sp.psfMagErr_i, sp.psfMagErr_z, sp.dered_u, sp.dered_g, sp.dered_r, sp.dered_i, sp.dered_z FROM SpecPhoto AS sp   INNER JOIN photoObjAll AS p ON sp.objid = p.objid  WHERE   class = &&& AND sp.zWarning = # AND sp.z># AND sp.z < =# AND p.clean=#
